--- TESTCASE Get All Divisions By Company - Success - 200 OK

--- HTTP
## TEST-EXPECT-STATUS: [200]
## TEST-HAS-BODY
GET {{ApiBaseUrl}}{{DivisionsSection}}/by-company/{{CompanyId}}

--- TEST
await tp.Test("Response should contain the previously created division.", async () =>
{
    var json = await tp.Response.Content.ReadAsStringAsync();
    var divisions = Newtonsoft.Json.JsonConvert.DeserializeObject<List<dynamic>>(json);

    NotNull(divisions);
    dynamic first = divisions[0];
    Equal("Software Development", (string)first.name);
    Equal("SWDEV", (string)first.code);
});

--- END


--- TESTCASE Get All Divisions By Company - Nonexistent Company - 404 Not Found

--- HTTP
## TEST-EXPECT-STATUS: [404]
GET {{ApiBaseUrl}}{{DivisionsSection}}/by-company/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

--- END
